; This has been extracted from
; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/linux/lxc-top.md

% lxc-top, linux

# Start `lxc-top`
lxc-top

# Adjust update interval
lxc-top <__d___delay_> <5>

# Sort by [n]ame, [c]pu use, [b]lock I/O, [m]emory, or [k]ernel memory
lxc-top <__s___sort_> <n_c_b_m_k>
